callChangedEvent

public void callChangedEvent(javax.telephony.events.CallEv[] eventList)
This handles the events not currently listened for by the Listener architecture. These include:
  • CallCtlTermConnHeldEv
  • CallCtlTermConnTalkingEv
All other events are eaten with the assumption that the corresponding listener event is also thrown.
Tags copied from interface: javax.telephony.CallObserver
Parameters:
eventList - The list of Call events.
